
{"AF":{"title":"The Longest Ride","summary":"It's a long ride","poster":"http://titan.csit.rmit.edu.au/~s3455338/wp/a2/movies/lride.jpg","trailer":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mjMYiLqsj1Q","rating":"https:\/\/titan.csit.rmit.edu.au\/~e54061\/wp\/movie-service\/image4.jpeg","description":["Former bull-riding champion Luke (Scott Eastwood) and college student Sophia (Britt Robertson) are in love, but conflicting paths and ideals threaten to tear them apart: Luke hopes to make a comeback on the rodeo circuit, and Sophia is about to embark on her dream job in New York's art world. As the couple ponder their romantic future, they find inspiration in Ira (Alan Alda), an elderly man whose decades-long romance with his beloved wife withstood the test of time."],"sessions":{"Monday":"6pm","Tuesday":"6pm","Saturday":"3pm","Sunday":"3pm"}},
"CH":{"title":"Shaun The Sheep","summary":"Sheeping around","poster":"http://titan.csit.rmit.edu.au/~s3455338/wp/a2/movies/shaun.jpg","trailer":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tQvwiOWpj7o","rating":"https:\/\/titan.csit.rmit.edu.au\/~e54061\/wp\/movie-service\/image1.jpeg","description":["From Aardman, the creators of Wallace & Gromit and Chicken Run, comes the highly anticipated big screen debut of Shaun the Sheep. When Shaun decides to take the day off and have some fun, he gets a little more action than he baa-rgained for! Shaun's mischief accidentally causes the Farmer to be taken away from the farm, so it's up to Shaun and the flock to travel to the Big City to rescue him. Will Shaun find the Farmer in the strange and unfamiliar world of the City before he's lost forever? Join Shaun and the flock on their hilarious, action-packed adventure in Shaun the Sheep the Movie."],"sessions":{"Monday":"1pm","Tuesday":"1pm","Wednesday":"6pm","Thursday":"6pm","Friday":"6pm","Saturday":"12pm","Sunday":"12pm"}},"RC":{"title":"Get Hard","summary":"Getting real hard","poster":"http://titan.csit.rmit.edu.au/~s3455338/wp/a2/movies/gethard.jpg","trailer":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lEqrpuU9fYI","rating":"https:\/\/titan.csit.rmit.edu.au\/~e54061\/wp\/movie-service\/image3.jpeg","description":["When obscenely rich hedge-fund manager James (Will Ferrell) is convicted of fraud and sentenced to a stretch in San Quentin, the judge gives him one month to get his affairs in order. Knowing that he won't survive more than a few minutes in prison on his own, James desperately turns to Darnell (Kevin Hart) -- a black businessman who's never even had a parking ticket -- for help. As Darnell puts James through the wringer, both learn that they were wrong about many things, including each other."],"sessions":{"Monday":"9pm","Tuesday":"9pm","Wednesday":"1pm","Thursday":"1pm","Friday":"1pm","Saturday":"6pm","Sunday":"6pm"}},"AC":{"title":"Fast 7","summary":"How fast are you?","poster":"http://titan.csit.rmit.edu.au/~s3455338/wp/a2/movies/fast7.jpg","trailer":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Skpu5HaVkOc","rating":"https:\/\/titan.csit.rmit.edu.au\/~e54061\/wp\/movie-service\/image3.jpeg","description":["After defeating international terrorist Owen Shaw, Dominic Toretto (Vin Diesel), Brian O'Conner (Paul Walker) and the rest of the crew have separated to return to more normal lives. However, Deckard Shaw (Jason Statham), Owen's older brother, is thirsty for revenge. A slick government agent offers to help Dom and company take care of Shaw in exchange for their help in rescuing a kidnapped computer hacker who has developed a powerful surveillance program."],"sessions":{"Wednesday":"9pm","Thursday":"9pm","Friday":"9pm","Saturday":"9pm","Sunday":"9pm"}}}